{"text_id":204352,"tokens":["Title",":"," Modelling"," the"," Cl","ump","ing","-","Induced"," Polar","imetric"," Variability"," of"," Hot"," Star"," Winds","\n\n","Abstract",":","\n","In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigate"," the"," polar","imetric"," variability"," induced"," by"," clump","ing"," in"," the"," winds"," of"," hot"," stars","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," the"," complex"," wind"," structures"," and"," their"," impact"," on"," observed"," polarization"," signals",","," which"," are"," crucial"," for"," interpreting"," the"," mass","-","loss"," rates"," and"," evolutionary"," paths"," of"," these"," stars","."," We"," employ"," a"," sophisticated"," radiative"," transfer"," code"," to"," simulate"," the"," polarization"," signatures"," of"," clump","ed"," stellar"," winds","."," By"," incorporating"," realistic"," wind"," clump","ing"," parameters",","," we"," model"," the"," time","-","dependent"," polar","imetric"," variability"," and"," analyze"," the"," resulting"," polarization"," light"," curves","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," generating"," synthetic"," polarization"," data"," for"," a"," range"," of"," clump","ing"," factors"," and"," comparing"," these"," with"," observed"," polar","imetric"," variability"," in"," hot"," stars","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," that"," clump","ing"," significantly"," enhances"," the"," polar","imetric"," variability",","," with"," distinct"," signatures"," that"," correlate"," with"," the"," clump","ing"," parameters","."," We"," find"," that"," higher"," clump","ing"," factors"," lead"," to"," increased"," polarization"," amplitudes"," and"," more"," pronounced"," variability"," patterns","."," These"," findings"," underscore"," the"," importance"," of"," accounting"," for"," wind"," clump","ing"," in"," polar","imetric"," studies"," of"," hot"," stars","."," Our"," work"," provides"," a"," framework"," for"," future"," observational"," and"," theoretical"," investigations",","," aiming"," to"," refine"," the"," models"," of"," stellar"," wind"," clump","ing"," and"," improve"," the"," accuracy"," of"," mass","-","loss"," rate"," determinations","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4o","label":1}